blog.name: fallnangelcreations
blog.title: FallnAngel Creations
blog.description:
I am Falln. This is my:
★ Multi-Muse Ask Blog
★ Multi-Muse Roleplay Blog
★ Personal Blog
-I am an artist, photographer, cosplayer, and giant nerd.
Here I will post my art, photography, cosplays, & works in progress.
As well as reblogging things that interest me (or my muses).
You are welcome to Ask me any questions!
Whether you're curious about me, have a cosplay question, horror movie question, etc... Come at me!

If you have a question for a character of mine, you're welcome to Ask them here, and they will reply (in character)!
*Make sure to say who the question is for, otherwise I will be the one answering.

You do not have to be a roleplayer to ask my muses questions, anyone is welcome!
★Ask Replies can be found here
★RP Rules & Info can be found here
★RP Character List can be found here
If you're on mobile & need a link to any part of my blog, let me know!
The links above should work on mobile!
My main fandoms are: Supernatural, Red Dead Redemption 2, Marvel, Tolkien, Labyrinth, Black Butler, Stranger Things, and Horror Movies, among others.

Disclaimer: Because of my involvement in Horror; frightening, morbid, violent, and bloody imagery will be posted here at random. This is the only warning I will give.

summary: after that iron man issue my dash is virtually impossible to navigate, every dang iron man fan is sporting an icon with schiti’s...
body:
after that iron man issue my dash is virtually impossible to navigate, every dang iron man fan is sporting an icon with schiti’s art and these three colors, i cant tell my posts from someone else’s posts, its like all Tumblr is just one person yelling and celebrating Tony Stark, the Canon Bi™, all day long,,,

its fucking great.

title: We're Still Here

by Tempestas_D_Uzu

The first time he met her, he was twenty and she was twenty-four; this meeting makes him change his perceptions of Toni Stark, and he changes his mind a few more times afterwards. It’s not until a decade later that he starts falling in love.

Despite everything they had gone through, they still stood firm.
